t)\\right)$ bits of space and the communication is $O\\left(\n\\log m \\left(\\,\\log n +\\log^3 m (\\log\\log m)^2 \\,\\right)\\right)$. The update\ntime of the verifier per symbol received is $O(\\log^2 m)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2014 06:31:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-28"}
