nt. Precise asymptotic expressions for\nthe particle-density, and coagulation rate are given.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2014 13:36:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Oct 2014 09:02:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
